Program: Outlook
Title: Abdul Haji: Hero of Westgate Attack
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01n5v7r
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 19 Dec 2013
A hero of the Westgate mall attack in Nairobi. Kenyan-Somali Abdul Haji went in to find his brother and ended up rescuing hundreds of people. Latvian Velga Vitola raised a brown bear cub in her house - alongside her two young children. And the acclaimed Dutch violinist, Janine Jansen, on making music with her family. Photo: Reuters/Goran Tomasevic. Show less